I am thrilled with this product.  It is a box of six pouches, with a dry, oatmeal-type product.  I was worried that this product might have soy.  But after reading the ingredients, I saw no soy.  Here are the ingredients:  whole grain oats, sugar, natural flavor, and salt.  It is gluten-free.

The taste is superb.  I tasted the maple and brown sugar.  Also, there are small oat flakes, which make it that much better, and give it texture.  I love oat flakes.

I love products such as these.  They are so versatile;
